nodes.text: Oecax was a male Ithorian chef who lived at the time of the Galactic Civil War. He worked in the Nashal cantina on Talus.

Oecax appeared as a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
